options.formula:
IF(
  OR(
    REGEX_MATCH({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) \\([A-Z]\\) (?i:Introduced|Introduced and)'),
    REGEX_MATCH({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) - INTRODUCED')
  ),
  IF(
    AND(
      REGEX_MATCH({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) \\([A-Z]\\) (?i:Introduced|Introduced and)'),
      REGEX_MATCH({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) - INTRODUCED')
    ),
    IF(
      VALUE(SUBSTITUTE(REGEX_EXTRACT({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) \\([A-Z]\\) (?i:Introduced|Introduced and)'), "/", "")) > 
      VALUE(SUBSTITUTE(REGEX_EXTRACT({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) - INTRODUCED'), "/", "")),
      REGEX_EXTRACT({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) \\([A-Z]\\) (?i:Introduced|Introduced and)'),
      REGEX_EXTRACT({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) - INTRODUCED')
    ),
    IF(
      REGEX_MATCH({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) \\([A-Z]\\) (?i:Introduced|Introduced and)'),
      REGEX_EXTRACT({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) \\([A-Z]\\) (?i:Introduced|Introduced and)'),
      REGEX_EXTRACT({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) - INTRODUCED')
    )
  ),
  0
)

options.formula:
IF(
  OR(
    REGEX_MATCH({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Signed by|Overridden)'),
    REGEX_MATCH({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:SIGNED|OVERRIDDEN)')
  ),
  IF(
    AND(
      REGEX_MATCH({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Signed by|Overridden)'),
      REGEX_MATCH({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:SIGNED|OVERRIDDEN)')
    ),
    IF(
      VALUE(SUBSTITUTE(
        IF(
          REGEX_MATCH({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Signed by)'),
          REGEX_EXTRACT({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Signed by)'),
          REGEX_EXTRACT({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Overridden)')
        ), "/", "")
      ) > 
      VALUE(SUBSTITUTE(
        IF(
          REGEX_MATCH({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:SIGNED)'),
          REGEX_EXTRACT({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:SIGNED)'),
          REGEX_EXTRACT({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:OVERRIDDEN)')
        ), "/", "")
      ),
      IF(
        REGEX_MATCH({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Signed by)'),
        REGEX_EXTRACT({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Signed by)'),
        REGEX_EXTRACT({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Overridden)')
      ),
      IF(
        REGEX_MATCH({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:SIGNED)'),
        REGEX_EXTRACT({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:SIGNED)'),
        REGEX_EXTRACT({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:OVERRIDDEN)')
      )
    ),
    IF(
      REGEX_MATCH({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Signed by|Overridden)'),
      IF(
        REGEX_MATCH({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Signed by)'),
        REGEX_EXTRACT({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Signed by)'),
        REGEX_EXTRACT({fldSGA2dzs3i1nGrD}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) (?:\\([A-Z]\\) )?(?i:Overridden)')
      ),
      IF(
        REGEX_MATCH({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '(?s).*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:SIGNED)'),
        REGEX_EXTRACT({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:SIGNED)'),
        REGEX_EXTRACT({fldHxBUTK36lRrViy}, '.*?(\\d{2}/\\d{2}/\\d{4}) -? (?i:OVERRIDDEN)')
      )
    )
  ),
  ""
)
